"{\"uid\": \"washingtontimes.com-news-2024-aug-3-chileans-advance-in-olympic-beach-volleyball-when-\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS-Chileadvanced to the knockout round of the Paris Olympics beach volleyball tournament on Saturday when Canada's Dan Dearing withdrew from their lucky loser match after three points because of a back injury.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 109, \"end\": 115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.935769845052893, \"rank\": 0.0493152723608336, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's part of sport.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes injuries happen.\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously horrific timing,\\\" said Dearing's partner, Sam Schachter.\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Schachter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Schachter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Schachter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Schachter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a nightmare for Dan and me and we want to be able to share that moment with our families and the crowd and get that Olympic spirit.\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, obviously, it did not happen today.\\\"\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dearing sustained the injury during practice on Saturday morning.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He and Schachter took the sand for the match that pits third-place teams from pool play against each other to fill out the final spots in the round of 16.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After three points, withChilewinning two, it became obvious to Dearing that he could not continue.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 832, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, we are frustrated,\\\" Schachter said.\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We want to be able to compete.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's super-disappointing that we were not able to get Dan's back to a place where he can compete.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But we really tried our hardest.\\\"\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chileadvances to the round of 16 against one of the pool winners.\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Esteban Grimalt, who teams with his cousin, Marco Grimalt, said the teams are friends who trained together when they first arrived inParis.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esteban_Grimalt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Esteban Grimalt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esteban_Grimalt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esteban_Grimalt\"}, {\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marco_Grimalt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marco Grimalt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marco_Grimalt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marco_Grimalt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not the best way, of course.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a shame,\\\" Esteban Grimalt said.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esteban_Grimalt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Esteban Grimalt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esteban_Grimalt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esteban_Grimalt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was really unexpected and really sad, actually, because we saw the pain - not just the physical pain, also the emotional pain.\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's hard to see a friend like that.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we hope, fast recovery and play again and in the next years.\\\"\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 The Washington Times, LLC.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9998689648662051, \"rank\": 0.00013104791569443783, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEE MORE VIDEOS  Where's Islamic extremism in National Guard shooting discussion?\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"score\": 0.9867651982632237, \"rank\": 0.012701771373729786, \"text\": \"Islamic extremism\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\"}, {\"begin\": 1655, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Guard_of_Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.989381872460621, \"rank\": 0.003916858393191504, \"text\": \"National Guard\", \"types\": [], \"w